node.text:
WIN 5k CASH + SONY CAMERA @willandbear MOMENTS CAPTURED 2021

Photographers, storytellers, filmmakers, and picture takers of every description, in any place. We invite you to share your moments captured for the chance to win!

Link in bio to enter now and win 10k worth of prizes! Score 5k cash + a @sonyalpha.anz Alpha 7C + 29-60mm kit lens + Master Class with @stefan_haworth 

Entries open worldwide! The contest closed at midnight on 21st Sept AEST. Full T&C's on the entry page. 

Thanks to last years artist submissions that were used to create this year's promo video!
@lindsayremigio @willpalmeer @ryan_borne @matt_tsangg @mooskicreative @wanderwithjamie
@loredvana @jakeyboy91 @juliedrummen @jaclyn_gittus @dreambagstory @andreacaruso @ellegillett @barneyjones_ @all.about.adventure @annabelbarratt @becky.jenkins @samuel_rutherford @renmcgann @alexbascuasphoto
